      "date": "2012-09-07 02:27:43.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\n> Tests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/366d342e-f878-11e1-986b-52540035b04c). Ran 12 tests. No failures.\n\nSKIP: sanity test_103 skipping SLOW test 103\n\nThe \"envdefinitions=SLOW=yes\" did not work.",
