          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-1823 kernel: enable kernel debug options",
        "message": "LU-1823 kernel: enable kernel debug options\n\nThis patch enables the following debug options:\nCONFIG_DEBUG_SLAB\nCONFIG_DEBUG_SLAB_LEAK\nCONFIG_DEBUG_SPINLOCK\nCONFIG_DEBUG_SPINLOCK_SLEEP\nCONFIG_DEBUG_STACK_USAGE\n\nIt also adds a check_slab_corruption() function into the\ntest framework to detect the slab corruption error.\n\nTest-Parameters: envdefinitions=SLOW=yes testlist=sanity\n\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <jian.yu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I0dda6f34e0f23765a2204ad0d263426ff29d0abd\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
